    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下在线教育平台的课堂互动流程，特别是学生抢答和计分的逻辑。我想从学生数据库开始，到课堂服务，再到LMS门户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是StudentDB，然后连到ClassroomService这个判断节点？ClassroomService是菱形还是矩形？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "ClassroomService是判断节点，用菱形。学生进入课堂后，系统要检查是否允许访问，然后流转到LMS门户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画好了：StudentDB → ClassroomService（菱形）→ LMS门户。接下来LMS门户要分支吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，LMS门户这里有个关键判断：如果学生有权限访问内容，就走到ContentCDN；如果没有，就进入另一个分支叫OtherFamilyChance，相当于给其他学生机会。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "OtherFamilyChance"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "OtherFamilyChance也是指向StudentDB吗？还是独立的节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OtherFamilyChance",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "OtherFamilyChance本质上是回到学生池的概念，可以标注为Education_StudentDB类型。不过这里我需要修正一下——它应该指向OtherFamilyRespondingAtStart这个子流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OtherFamilyChance",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我把OtherFamilyChance从直接连StudentDB改为进入子流程OtherFamilyRespondingAtStart。现在处理Yes分支：ContentCDN之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OtherFamilyChance",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ContentCDN之后进入RoundStart子流程，这是核心抢答环节。里面先有CheckResponse，由GradeSync服务判断是否有学生响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "RoundStart",
        "CheckResponse",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
